   <div class="teaser_fmt"> 
    <h3>Bipolar Disorder Overview</h3> 
    <p>Bipolar disorder, with its extreme mood swings from depression to mania, used to be called manic depressive disorder. Bipolar disorder is very serious and can cause risky behavior, even suicidal tendencies, and can be treated with therapy and medication.</p> 
   </div>
